title: UK Subs: The Last Will And Testament Of UK Subs
overview: The UK Subs deliver a blistering live set of their classic hits at the 100 Club in London, England in the fall of 2023. Charlie Harper, Alvin Gibbs, Steve Staughan and Stefan Haublein - deliver a blistering 70 minute live set of their best known classics in front of their rabid and loyal fans at the 100 Club in London, England in the fall of 2023.
